data.description: View The Space Coast from your porch with a view of NASA launches and marvel at manatees during Florida sunsets (sometimes simultaneously). This modernized 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo boasts an updated kitchen with quartz countertops, a Bosh refrigerator, and a Whirlpool dishwasher. Smart home features, effortlessly controlling locks, thermostat, and vibrant lighting. A recently installed AC ensures comfort, backed by a warranty until 2031. Nestled just under a mile from the pristine beach, the community offers a sparkling pool, inviting picnic areas, a fitness zone, and direct kayak access. Boat enthusiasts can avail slots for a fee.
